{
  "texts": [
    "The Metaverse is a virtual environment where people can interact in digital spaces, creating a more immersive experience.",
    "It is a persistent network of 3D virtual worlds that will eventually serve as the gateway to most online experiences and will also significantly impact the physical world.",
    "These ideas, previously confined to science fiction and video games, are poised to revolutionize various industries, such as finance, healthcare, education, and consumer products (Huynh-The et al. 2022).",
    "Metaverse and Artificial Intelligence (AI) are two rapidly evolving technologies that are poised to revolutionize the way we live, work, and interact with each other.",
    "The Metaverse is a virtual world that is being created by merging the physical and digital worlds and is expected to provide immersive experiences and a new platform for social interaction."
  ]
}